project: Instructions:                                                                How to play: You can play by using the arrow keys to go up, down, left, or right. Your goal is to go through all of the rings. At the end of each level there will be a door to go through in order to get to the next level will see that in the top left corner on top of the lives, if you touch an obstacle at the 3rd level, you start losing lives.. You have 3 lives and with each level of the game, it will get harder and you will get more lives. You can get more lives by collecting bananas from rings. After every level your live count will reset. Also the purple minions are evil if you touch them or if they touch u u die.
